sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Workstation
    participant OC as oc adm must-gather /<br/>kubectl Job
    participant Pod as must-gather Pod<br/>(gather.sh)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Helm as helm CLI<br/>(local exec)
    participant FS as /must-gather<br/>Local Filesystem

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over User,FS: Flow 1: OpenShift must-gather Collection
        User->>OC: oc adm must-gather --image=...
        OC->>Pod: Creates must-gather Pod
        Pod->>K8sAPI: Detect K8s distribution<br/>GET infrastructures.config.openshift.io<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>Pod: OpenShift detected
        Pod->>K8sAPI: Collect platform resources<br/>GET DSCInitialization, DataScienceCluster<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>Pod: Platform CRs

        par Parallel Component Collection
            Pod->>K8sAPI: gather_serving.sh<br/>GET InferenceService, ServingRuntime, AuthConfig<br/>+ DEFAULT_RESOURCES (Gateway, HTTPRoute, EnvoyFilter)
            Pod->>K8sAPI: gather_data_science_pipelines.sh<br/>GET DataSciencePipelinesApplication, Workflow
            Pod->>K8sAPI: gather_notebooks.sh<br/>GET Notebook, ImageStream
            Pod->>K8sAPI: gather_dashboard.sh<br/>GET OdhDashboardConfig, AcceleratorProfile
            Pod->>K8sAPI: gather_kuberay.sh<br/>GET RayCluster, RayJob, RayService
            Pod->>K8sAPI: gather_kueue.sh<br/>GET ClusterQueue, LocalQueue, Workload
            Pod->>K8sAPI: gather_kfto.sh<br/>GET PyTorchJob, TrainJob, TrainingRuntime
            Pod->>K8sAPI: gather_mr.sh<br/>GET ModelRegistry
            Pod->>K8sAPI: gather_trustyai.sh<br/>GET TrustyAIService, LMEvalJob, EvalHub
            Pod->>K8sAPI: gather_feastoperator.sh<br/>GET FeatureStore
            Pod->>K8sAPI: gather_mlflow.sh<br/>GET MLflow
            Pod->>K8sAPI: gather_sparkoperator.sh<br/>GET SparkApplication, SparkConnect
            Pod->>K8sAPI: gather_models_as_a_service.sh<br/>GET MaaSModelRef, MaaSAuthPolicy, Tenant
        end

        K8sAPI-->>Pod: Component CRs + Logs
        Pod->>FS: Write collected data
        Pod-->>OC: Collection complete
        OC->>User: oc rsync collected data
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over User,FS: Flow 2: xKS (Non-OpenShift) Collection
        User->>K8sAPI: kubectl create Job must-gather
        K8sAPI->>Pod: Job creates Pod
        Pod->>K8sAPI: detect_k8s_distro<br/>Kernel version / Provider ID / OS image
        K8sAPI-->>Pod: AKS / CKS / generic K8s
        Pod->>K8sAPI: kubectl_inspect (auto-discovery)<br/>GET api-resources → iterate all types<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>Pod: All namespaced + cluster resources
        Pod->>K8sAPI: Collect pod logs<br/>GET pods/log (current + previous)
        K8sAPI-->>Pod: Container logs
        Pod->>FS: Write collected data
        Note over Pod: sleep 600 (wait for user)
        User->>Pod: kubectl cp must-gather-pod:/must-gather ./
    end

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over User,FS: Flow 3: Helm Release Value Collection
        Pod->>Helm: helm get values rhoai/rhaii
        Helm->>K8sAPI: Read Helm secrets<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>Helm: Helm release data
        Helm-->>Pod: Values YAML
        Pod->>Helm: helm get manifest rhoai/rhaii
        Helm-->>Pod: Rendered manifests
        Pod->>FS: Write to $DST_DIR/namespaces/<ns>/helm/
    end

    rect rgb(243, 229, 245)
        Note over User,FS: Flow 4: LLM-D Collection (within main flow)
        Pod->>K8sAPI: gather_llmd.sh<br/>GET LLMInferenceService, InferencePool,<br/>InferenceObjective, Gateway, HTTPRoute
        K8sAPI-->>Pod: LLM-D resources

        par LLM-D Dependency Collection (parallel)
            Pod->>K8sAPI: cert-manager.sh<br/>GET Certificate, Issuer, ClusterIssuer
            Pod->>K8sAPI: sail.sh<br/>GET Istio, VirtualService, DestinationRule,<br/>PeerAuthentication, AuthorizationPolicy
            Pod->>K8sAPI: lws.sh<br/>GET LeaderWorkerSet
        end

        Pod->>K8sAPI: gather_cluster.sh<br/>GET nodes, cluster-info, cluster-scoped CRs
        Pod->>K8sAPI: gather_o11y.sh<br/>GET ServiceMonitor, PodMonitor, PrometheusRule<br/>or ama-metrics pods (AKS)
        K8sAPI-->>Pod: Dependency + cluster data
        Pod->>FS: Write LLM-D data
    end
